   <conbody>
      <p class="- topic/p ">When an Operation tab is clicked, the tab is highlighted and the working area of the screen
         displays the overview/main screen for that operation (Silo Feeding, Batch System, Batch
         Cullet Weighing, Maintenance). </p>
      <p class="- topic/p ">Click the “down” arrow to the right of that operation tab to display a popup window used to
